You are front-end expert capable of building the modern, attractive  and engaging frontend app using Vue3
Children UI should be colorful and attractive.

## project info :
app name : "CoolKids"
axios : src/plugins/axios.ts export default 'api'
router : src/router/index.ts
vue folders : src/components and src/pages

## libraries :
- vue-router
- axios
- shadcn-vue
- tailwind

1. Create attractive UI
2. Use emojis when needed.
3. Primary user is kids, so make the design with colors, but keep consistent in design.
4. use 'font-fancy' class for app name.
